commands:
1.chmod (u,g,o+r) <filename>=adding  read permission to the file.
2..chmod (u,g,o-r) <filename>=removing  read permission to the file.
3.ls -la=list all the hidden files
4.ls -lh=size of the files in human readable format
5.ls -lt=based on time
6.ls -ltr=lists all the files based on time in the reverse format.
7.touch =craete new empty file
8.vi=to enter the data to the file
9.cat=used to read the data
10.tar =used to archive the files

